OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRisk of the odd mist or fog
OL,6,Fpatch at first for Shetland. Otherwise
OL,7,Fmostly dry and bright, but rain
OL,8,Farriving for Orkney by late afternoon.
OL,9,FLight winds, turning breezier later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FHeavy rain across Orkney at
OL,12,Ffirst will spread to Shetland through
OL,13,Fthe evening. Overnight, the rain will
OL,14,Fbecome more patchy, though it will
OL,15,Fremain rather cloudy and murky.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
