OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy with patchy rain
OL,6,Fclearing during the morning for
OL,7,FShetland. Otherwise a bright day with
OL,8,Fsunny spells and scattered showers.
OL,9,FStrong winds, occasional gales for
OL,10,FShetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAn
OL,13,Fchangeable westerly pattern brings
OL,14,Fvariable cloud and scattered showers
OL,15,Fduring this period, with some sunshine
OL,16,Fat times but often windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
